, and the USPS Informed Delivery digest.\n\nI should also include ngrok since it's marked as updates with the unread indicator. Let me grab the unread messages from today to see if there's anything else worth surfacing, then I'll organize these into the email section format.","thinkingSignature":"ad3e6cb0d463ffd42645e0ddb63f8dc5e651fe625ecd9a4ad1507f5ed0c4a520"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\nNow I have all the data I need. Let me send the sections one at a time.\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_h3baru57pycy_1","name":"message","arguments":{"action":"send","message":"Good morning, Bobby! ☀️\n\nThursday, April 30, 2026\n\nHere's what we've got going on for today…","target":"8212808444"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":847,"output":501,"cacheRead":36160,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":37508,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1777541665505,"responseId":"06425521ad10be7140345849103344b0"},{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_h3baru57pycy_1","toolName":"message","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"ok\": true,\n  \"messageId\": \"23956\",\n  \"chatId\": \"8212808444\"\n}"}],"details":{"ok":true,"messageId":"23956","chatId":"8212808444"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1777541680939},{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now Section 2 - Weather","thinkingSignature":"a62bea8974717ac46a17634debdac5c075aa6140319f0dd4898b1b02f0da38e6"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_s0y7h3v065y3_1","name":"message","arguments":{"action":"send","message":"🌤️ Knoxville Weather — April 30\n\nNOW: 59° (feels like 59°)\nHIGH: 72° | LOW: 48°\nWIND: 6mph | HUMIDITY: 82% | UV: 0 (Low) | RAIN: 0%\n\n⏰ HOUR BY HOUR:\n9AM:  59° ☀️\n12PM: 65° ☀️\n3PM:  69° ☀️\n6PM:  62° ☀️\n9PM:  53° ☀️\n\n💡 VERDICT: Pack a light jacket — mild but breezy.","target":"8212808444"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model"