in.","📝 REMINDERS\n\n• Coloring Book — sell\n• Email apartments (Fishkill, Royal Cove & Ridgefield)\n• Go through all mail in Xfinity bag with Logan\n• Put all bills in the Family Calendar\n• Work on recipe app idea","🦞 OPENCLAW UPDATE AVAILABLE\n\nNew version: npm 2026.4.27\nChannel: stable\n\nDo you want me to update? (yes/no)","💡 WAYS I CAN HELP TODAY\n\n1. Pay your Apple Card bill right now ($64) — it's due at 9 AM\n2. Check the Xfinity refund email and confirm the amount/status\n3. Review those ZipRecruiter job matches — Diag Partners and Aspen Dental look relevant\n4. Email the apartments (Fishkill, Royal Cove, Ridgefield) — knock out that reminder today\n5. Put all those outstanding bills on the Family Calendar so nothing slips again\n6. Check on the PetScreening \"Non-Compliant Pet\" issue — sounds urgent\n7. Draft a response to ngrok about those seven new features they're asking for feedback on"],"messagingToolSentMediaUrls":[],"messagingToolSentTargets":[{"tool":"message","provider":"message","to":"8212808444"},{"tool":"message","provider":"message","to":"8212808444"},{"tool":"message","provider":"message","to":"8212808444"},{"tool":"message","provider":"message","to":"8212808444"},{"tool":"message","provider":"message","to":"8212808444"},{"tool":"message","provider":"message","to":"8212808444"},{"tool":"message","provider":"message","to":"8212808444"},{"tool":"message","provider":"message","to":"8212808444"}]}}
